this repo hosts as a `formal_proof` target. `scripts/check_axioms.sh` builds
this file and fails CI if any line reports an unfinished proof outside the
allowed set `[propext, Classical.choice, Quot.sound]`.

When you add a solved formal-proof target, add its module import and a
`#print axioms` line in the manifest-tracked section here, plus a matching entry
in `proofs.yaml`. Conditional research surfaces may be audited below without
being advertised as solved proof targets.
-/
